<p>The authors thank the MACS participants, without whom this and many other studies would not have been possible. Data in this article were collected by the Multicenter AIDS Cohort Study (MACS), now the MACS/WIHS Combined Cohort Study (MWCCS).</p></section><section id="s012"><h2 class="pmc_sec_title">Authors' Contribution</h2>
<p>Conception and design: S.K.H., A.G., O.M.-M., and L.P.J. Acquisition of data: O.M.-M. and L.P.J. Analysis and interpretation of data: S.K.H., A.G., O.M.-M., and L.P.J. Writing, review, and/or revision of the article: all authors. Study supervision: L.P.J.</p></section><section id="s013"><h2 class="pmc_sec_title">Author Disclosure Statement</h2>
<p>No competing financial interests exist.</p></section><section id="s014"><h2 class="pmc_sec_title">Funding Information</h2>
